applicants do n't qualify for citizenship they can redeem the bonds but if they do they can become citizens and the bond is to be repaid without interest in 10 years. The plan is aimed mainly at residents of <LOCATION> Hong </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Kong </LOCATION>, a British colony that is to revert to <LOCATION> China </LOCATION> in 1997. Many <LOCATION> Hong </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Kong </LOCATION> residents are expected to flee the colony rather than accept control by communist <LOCATION> China </LOCATION>. <PERSON> Esquivel </PERSON> has said that during the past five years prices for sugar, fruits and other major exports have been stable and foreign investments and tourism have doubled. <LOCATION> Belize </LOCATION> has a bicameral legislature with an elected <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Representatives </ORGANIZATION> and appointed <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION>. The house determines which party will form a new government. <LOCATION> Belize </LOCATION>, smaller than <LOCATION> Connecticut </LOCATION>, is on the Central American mainland but maintains closer cultural ties with other English-speaking former <LOCATION> British </LOCATION> colonies in the <LOCATION> Caribbean </LOCATION> than with its Spanish-speaking neighbors. Neighboring <LOCATION> Guatemala </LOCATION> maintains a territorial claim against <LOCATION> Belize </LOCATION>, formerly British <LOCATION> Honduras </LOCATION>, and British troops are stationed in the country in case of hostilities with <LOCATION> Guatemala </LOCATION>.
